Package de.coderarea.jrdp.protocol.ASN1 Description

ASN.1 - Abstract Syntax Notation One.
This package models ASN.1 data as Plain Old Java Objects (POJOs).
Author:
Sascha Biedermann
See Also:
ASN.1 encoding rules: Specification of Basic Encoding Rules (BER), Canonical Encoding Rules (CER) and Distinguished Encoding Rules (DER), ASN.1 encoding rules: Specification of Packed Encoding Rules (PER)
